title: The Cayo Perico Heist: Coming December 15 to GTA Online
tags: gta online|gta online update|gta 5 online|cayo perico heist|ps4|ps5|xbox series x|xbox one x|pc
description: It‚Äôs time to raise the stakes higher than ever before. You‚Äôve broken a convicted spy out of Bolingbroke Penitentiary. You‚Äôve saved the world from an egomaniacal tech billionaire. And you‚Äôve beaten the odds to drain a casino of its cash. This time, you‚Äôre taking on an entire island.Prepare to infiltrate the remote island compound of the world‚Äôs most notorious drug dealer in Grand Theft Auto Online‚Äôs biggest, most daring, and action-packed addition yet: The Cayo Perico Heist.It‚Äôs up to you to find a way to breach Cayo Perico, one of the most secure private islands in the entire world, evade or neutralize the heavily armed security forces stationed there, and escape with valuable evidence along with as much art, gold and drug money as you can carry.  Choose your tools. Choose your approach. Choose your crew ‚Äì or even go it entirely alone. Just make it back to Los Santos in one piece.The Cayo Perico Heist is the biggest GTA Online adventure ever, introducing an all-new exotic Heist location, with a brand-new approach to Heist design that features the ability to play everything solo or with up to three other players. Plus you can acquire new vehicles and tactical weapons, experience new social spaces to dance and party with friends and new world-class DJs, and listen to new radio stations with over 100 new songs. Oh, and a very large, very versatile, and very heavily armed submarine HQ with plenty of other surprises.  Stay tuned for more details as you prepare for The Cayo Perico Heist.Coming to PS4, Xbox One, PC, and via backward compatibility for PS5 / Xbox Series X|S.

description: Video shows how to make French toast. French toast ‚Äì one of the most popular homemade dishes in French cuisine. In France, they call French toast ‚Äì ‚ÄúPain Perdu‚Äù (it means lost bread). This recipe explains how to make French toast (SWEET) as a dessert course for breakfast. Using this original French toast recipe, you will make a tasty dessert in 8-10 min for breakfast. The main ingredients of recipe are bread, egg and milk. All other ingredients of this recipe for staffing and garnishing you can change on your own taste. Enjoy this easy and quick 1 min video recipe how to make original French toast from HowToMin!Sweet French toast Recipe:INGREDIENTS:‚Ä¢ 4 thick slices of baguette‚Ä¢ 1 large egg ‚Ä¢ 50ml (1.7 fl. oz.) milk or cream ‚Ä¢ 2 tbsp. sugar ‚Ä¢ 1/4 tsp cinnamon ‚Ä¢ pinch of salt ‚Ä¢ splash of vanilla extract ‚Ä¢ butter for cooking‚Ä¢ Greek yogurt, jam and Blueberries for garnishIMPORTANT:You can use fresh or stale bread for this recipe of the French toast. HOW TO MAKE FRENCH TOAST:Stir the egg with milk - 50ml (1.7 fl. oz.)Add sugar, salt, cinnamon and a drop of vanilla extract  Stir wellCut 4 thick (about 2 inch) slices of baguette (or any other stale bread)Pour the mix in a plateArrange the bread slices and leave them to soak for 2 minFlip the slices and leave them to soakHeat the pan and melt butterPlace the bread and sear 2 min from each sideSpread a cooking dish with butterCook in oven about 5-6 min 320ÀöF (160ÀöC)Garnish with Greek yogurt, blueberries and mint leavesEnjoy your tasty French toast!WEBSITE: https://howtomin.com FOLLOW US ON:INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/howtomin_com FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/howtomin/ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/howtomin_com  TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@howtomin

title: Celebrating Maria Tallchief
tags: [none]
description: In honor of Native American Heritage Month in the U.S., today‚Äôs video Doodle‚Äîcreated in partnership with Native American guest artists Lydia Cheshewalla, Chris Pappan, and Yatika Starr Fields‚Äî celebrates Maria Tallchief, member of the Osage Nation who was America‚Äôs first, major prima ballerina. Not only a trailblazer for Native American dancers, Tallchief is widely considered one of the country‚Äôs most influential ballerinas of all time. On this day in 2007, a bronze sculpture of Tallchief and four other Native American ballerinas was unveiled in Oklahoma at the Tulsa Historical Society in a piece titled ‚ÄúThe Five Moons‚Äù by artist Gary Henson. title: Fixing The UNFIXABLE: Squishy Makeovers from The Hopeless Bin
tags: squishy makeover|painting on things|tiktok painting|things to paint on|fun painting projects|how to fix squishies
description: Hey guys! Today I am doing a video that was honestly DEMANDED by some people in my comment sections recently üòÇ Many of you really wanted to see my attempt to Fix The Unfixable, sooooo, here I go. This special episode of squishy makeovers will be me attempting to fix and redecorate squishies from the WORST or worst. These extremely damaged squishies come from my hopeless bin and I was honestly not sure if they would ever make it out!Also, I am aware that this whole spamming of my comment setions kind of started a war between those who were doing it and those who thought it was really annoying üòÇ I appreciate those of you who didn't want me to be pressured into doing a video I didn't want to do! Don't worry, I'm happy to give it a try. And I appreciate getting video requests from you guys.DON'T FORGET ABOUT THE COUSIN DERP PLUSH!https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/AND The new Christmas apparel design is now available here:https://moriah-elizabeth.teespring.com/listing/special-holiday-collection?product=345_________FAQs__________1. CAN I SEND YOU SQUISHIES?So many generous people have sent me their unwanted squishies so I actually have a lot to work on already, BUT if you desperately want to, you can request my mailing address in the email ALLLL the way at down in the description (sorry for the traveling), make sure to read the disclaimer down there as well.2. ARE SQUISHIES RETURNED TO THE SENDERS AFTER THE MAKEOVER?No. These squishies  are sent as donations to the series because they were damaged, and no longer wanted. Everyone has been informed in advance that squishies would not be returned. It would be waaay too complicated/expensive and massively time consuming to keep track of everyone and return each squishy. I'm just one person! 3. WHAT PAINT DO YOU USE?I use fabric paint. Fabric paint is meant to stretch, so it is perfect for squishing! Any brand will work fine, but I mainly use Tulip. You can find it at Michaels, Hobby Lobby, A.C. Moore, Walmart, Joann Fabrics, and Online.5. WILL FABRIC PAINT CRACK?The matte fabric paint is more likely to crack after lots of squishing. Slick fabric paints never crack. But there are benefits to both. I usually mix the two paints together to get the best of both worlds.___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh üòÇ ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating, painting and general art videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). CURRENT SERIES:Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewersThrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard salesBake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real lifeCreate This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewersCraft Kit Testing: pretty self explanatory. testing craft kits.___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___Every Friday at 4:00pm ET: Alternating Squishy Makeovers, Thrift Makeovers, Craft Kit Reviews, Create This Book, Mail Openings and Miscellaneous crafts and DIYs____PURCHASE ME PRODUCTS____CREATE THIS BOOK:https://amzn.to/2vUerfICREATE THIS BOOK 2:https://amzn.to/2Nx2G9fME Custom Merchandise:https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/ME Pin & Sticker Shop:https://me-merch.myshopify.comME Printed Apparel and Accessories:https://moriah-elizabeth.teespring.com/____ME SOCIALS____INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/moriahelizabethofficial/TIKTOK:https://www.tiktok.com/@me.moriah.elizabethVISIT ME WEBSITE:https://www.moriahelizabeth.com/____CONTACT ME____EMAIL PICTURES OF YOUR ART (Create This Book or Fan art only please):Artwork@Moriah.videoFOR BUSINESS INQUIRIES/OPPORTUNITIES ONLY:moriah@nightmedia.co_____MAIL ME_____For sending squishies, Letters, or general fan mail, please contact: FANMAIL@MORIAH.VIDEO to request my P.O. box address (must be 13+ to send mail)ATTENTION: Unfortunately I can only respond to a small amount of people each week. This is to make sure that I get a reasonable amount of mail and can feature the maximum amount on camera. I apologize in advance if you do not hear back from me, I may not have even seen the message.
